T1  - Large-scale genome-wide meta-analysis of polycystic ovary syndrome suggests shared genetic architecture for different diagnosis criteria.
T3  - Erratum in: PLoS Genet. 2019 Dec 5;15(12):e1008517 PMID: 31805045 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31805045] Comment in: Gynecol Endocrinol. 2022 Aug;38(8):615-616 PMID: 35971943 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35971943]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1371/journal.pgen.1007813
A1  - Day, Felix
A1  - Karaderi, Tugce
A1  - Jones, Michelle R
A1  - Meun, Cindy
