T1  - Oral carnitine supplementation influences mental health parameters and biomarkers of oxidative stress in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial.
T3  - Expression of Concern in: Gynecol Endocrinol. 2023 Dec;39(1):1841983. doi: 10.1080/09513590.2020.1841983 PMID: 33174793 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33174793] Update in: Gynecol Endocrinol. 2023 Dec;39(1):1841983. doi: 10.1080/09513590.2020.1841983 PMID: 33174793 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33174793] Retraction in: Gynecol Endocrinol. 2024 Dec;40(1):2373613. doi: 10.1080/09513590.2024.2373613 PMID: 39001666 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/39001666]
