T1  - Preconception gynecological risk factors of postpartum depression among Japanese women: The Japan Environment and Children's Study (JECS).
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jad.2017.03.049
A1  - Muchanga, Sifa Marie Joelle
A1  - Yasumitsu-Lovell, Kahoko
A1  - Eitoku, Masamitsu
