T1  - Vitamin D and chronic diseases: the current state of the art.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s00204-016-1804-x
A1  - Muscogiuri, Giovanna
A1  - Altieri, Barbara
A1  - Annweiler, Cedric
